'''Soco-Jarel Spaceport''' was a large [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Socorro/Legends|Socorro]] administered by [[Aquato Boliscon]]. It rivaled [[Vakeyya]] in size.

